Name: Evren Kuzucuoglu
AboutMe:
It all started with programmable calculators and a seat at the back of the classroom. The typical math nerd (no glasses), I have evolved into an almost adult professional with a reasonable social life, a serious penchant for travelling and interests in various arts and sports.

I have worked as a computer software engineer several years in my native France, several years in Spain and again several years in UK where I now live, in an eclectic array of businesses where I have seen the good and the bad mixing up with the ugly without tampering my love for the international language of logic...
